[Episode 6]

4
00:00:16,280 --> 00:00:17,040
Governor.

5
00:00:17,080 --> 00:00:18,000
Someone just said

6
00:00:18,160 --> 00:00:19,880
a man took Ms. Yun upstairs.

7
00:00:19,960 --> 00:00:21,320
You can go back to the ceremony.

8
00:00:21,360 --> 00:00:22,200
We'll look for her.

9
00:00:22,320 --> 00:00:23,120
Shut up.

10
00:00:23,240 --> 00:00:24,200
Go find her.

11
00:00:24,280 --> 00:00:25,080
Yes.

12
00:00:30,720 --> 00:00:31,800
Relax.

13
00:00:31,880 --> 00:00:33,040
I will be very gentle.

14
00:00:34,120 --> 00:00:35,960
Governor, I guess she's on this floor.

15
00:00:36,200 --> 00:00:37,240
Split up and search.

16
00:00:38,200 --> 00:00:39,440
Shoot.

17
00:00:40,200 --> 00:00:41,520
They come so quickly.

18
00:00:57,920 --> 00:00:59,040
Are you alright?

19
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:23,000
Stay away from me.

20
00:01:26,600 --> 00:01:28,000
But you don't look well.

21
00:01:30,280 --> 00:01:31,360
I'm fine.

22
00:01:31,840 --> 00:01:32,880
It's none of your business.

23
00:01:34,960 --> 00:01:36,080
Alright.

24
00:01:36,760 --> 00:01:37,760
As I said,

25
00:01:38,880 --> 00:01:39,720
I'll leave you alone.

26
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:07,280
Don't look at me.

27
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:09,920
Why can't I look at you?

28
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:20,880
♪I'm waiting for the rain
to wet the city♪

29
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:24,040
♪At dusk♪

30
00:02:24,760 --> 00:02:28,640
♪As I ran into someone I missed
at the street corner♪

31
00:02:28,720 --> 00:02:31,800
♪Old memories flashed♪

32
00:02:32,440 --> 00:02:35,800
♪If I can shout that I miss you♪

33
00:02:35,880 --> 00:02:39,840
♪I'll be waiting for the sunshine
in the rain♪

34
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:42,280
♪If your heart is as cold as ice♪

35
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:43,000
Ji Lianyun.

36
00:02:43,200 --> 00:02:44,280
Come on.

37
00:02:44,560 --> 00:02:45,600
I'll take you to the hospital.

38
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:51,360
♪My heart will call for you♪

39
00:02:51,440 --> 00:02:55,200
♪Are you as resolute as I am♪

40
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:59,240
♪You wake me up to see you♪

41
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:02,360
♪I'm sure your heart will be soft♪

42
00:03:02,440 --> 00:03:05,080
♪You approach me in the name of love♪

43
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:06,720
No need to go to the hospital.

44
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:08,440
I only need

45
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:10,680
you.

46
00:03:10,480 --> 00:03:15,160
♪I have no regrets when being with you♪

47
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:17,880
♪And you're like the rising wind♪

48
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:21,760
♪I ask you not to leave me
in the name of love♪

49
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:26,200
♪Wind blows and we part ways in silence♪

50
00:03:26,600 --> 00:03:28,400
♪And you're like the cloud♪

51
00:03:28,600 --> 00:03:33,120
♪Moving closer or farther away from me♪

52
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:31,600
Last night,

53
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:32,360
we...

54
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:33,560
I don't remember

55
00:04:33,840 --> 00:04:34,760
about last night.

56
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:36,720
Okay then.

57
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:38,400
Guess what?

58
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:40,800
You were drugged last night.

59
00:04:41,280 --> 00:04:41,880
Luckily...

60
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:43,200
Enough.

61
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:47,360
Luckily, I saved you.

62
00:04:47,840 --> 00:04:49,400
To thank me,

63
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:51,400
you even tore my uniform.

64
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:54,840
Do you need me to help you remember?

65
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:56,400
No, I don't want to know.

66
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:58,840
You forget it too.

67
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:04,160
Why should I forget?

68
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:08,080
The traitor Ji Xianwen is your father.

69
00:05:15,400 --> 00:05:16,800
Ji Lianyun.

70
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:23,360
I can hide your identity.

71
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:24,880
In return,

72
00:05:25,320 --> 00:05:26,880
you stay by my side

73
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,680
just as a woman

74
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,640
in the dark.

75
00:05:30,840 --> 00:05:32,280
You will do

76
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:34,520
whatever I say.

77
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:37,960
Whatever.

78
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:41,120
After all, I have no choice,

79
00:05:42,280 --> 00:05:43,360
right?

80
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:12,600
Ji Lianyun, calm down.

81
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:14,400
Since you could leave him before,

82
00:06:14,440 --> 00:06:15,800
you can do it now.

83
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:17,520
Don't forget.

84
00:06:17,760 --> 00:06:20,320
Pin is still missing because of you.

85
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:23,160
And remember
you have more important things to do.

86
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:51,240
You two are a perfect match.

87
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:54,920
Shame on you.

88
00:06:55,200 --> 00:06:57,360
Today, you're doomed.

89
00:06:57,520 --> 00:06:58,560
You think killing me

90
00:06:58,600 --> 00:07:00,840
can cover up your dirty deeds forever?

91
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:06,240
Give up.

92
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:08,040
Be a good girl

93
00:07:08,520 --> 00:07:10,400
and give me the film.

94
00:07:13,080 --> 00:07:14,080
Speak!

95
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:15,720
Where is the film?

96
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:20,320
I have many films about you.

97
00:07:21,280 --> 00:07:23,360
I will never give them to you.

98
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:26,000
I'll let everyone know your dirty deeds.

99
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:33,920
Let's see if you'll ever get the chance
to tell them.

100
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:35,760
I warn you.

101
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:38,240
My patience is running out.

102
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,600
Speak!

103
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:41,480
Where is the film?

104
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:43,960
Hand it over,

105
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:45,800
and I'll kill you fast.

106
00:07:58,160 --> 00:07:59,960
So, no one admits, huh?

107
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:03,280
Well, you asked for it.

108
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:04,880
Three.

109
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:05,680
Governor.

110
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:07,080
We don't know anything.

111
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:09,440
We don't know
who kidnapped Ms. Yun Lian.

112
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:10,920
Two.

113
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:12,200
Please spare us.

114
00:08:12,520 --> 00:08:13,520
One.

115
00:08:17,520 --> 00:08:19,720
Where is Xue Zhihai?

116
00:08:47,680 --> 00:08:48,640
You're bleeding.

117
00:08:49,280 --> 00:08:50,080
Mr. Xue.

118
00:08:53,520 --> 00:08:54,120
Mr. Xue.

119
00:08:54,160 --> 00:08:55,040
Something is up.

120
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:56,160
Got it. You may go.

121
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:56,800
Yes.

122
00:08:57,240 --> 00:08:58,080
Get Changlin here

123
00:08:58,120 --> 00:08:58,800
