124
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:02,520
Let me patch you up.

125
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:18,880
What happened, Dongfeng?

126
00:09:24,400 --> 00:09:25,480
Well,

127
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:28,040
